WEBVTT

00:00:00.306 --> 00:00:02.456 A:middle
Congratulations on
finishing CapsimInbox!

00:00:03.036 --> 00:00:05.076 A:middle
Now that you've had a chance
to review your results,

00:00:05.456 --> 00:00:07.766 A:middle
let's talk about a few tips
that can boost the success

00:00:07.766 --> 00:00:09.276 A:middle
of your self-improvement
efforts.

00:00:10.046 --> 00:00:12.826 A:middle
The feedback you received
from CapsimInbox is valuable

00:00:13.066 --> 00:00:15.076 A:middle
because it assesses your
current skill levels

00:00:15.276 --> 00:00:16.716 A:middle
and provides the
objective feedback

00:00:16.716 --> 00:00:18.476 A:middle
that is necessary
for true development.

00:00:19.006 --> 00:00:21.486 A:middle
Learning how to improve your
skills - is a critical skill

00:00:21.486 --> 00:00:23.576 A:middle
in its own right,
and is important

00:00:23.576 --> 00:00:25.556 A:middle
for professionals at
all career stages.

00:00:26.446 --> 00:00:29.366 A:middle
To truly master a skill you have
to learn what that skill looks

00:00:29.366 --> 00:00:30.936 A:middle
like when it's effectively
performed.

00:00:31.586 --> 00:00:33.976 A:middle
Mastery also requires
that you frequently

00:00:33.976 --> 00:00:35.696 A:middle
and consistently
practice the skill,

00:00:36.486 --> 00:00:38.106 A:middle
which often involves
some trial and error.

00:00:39.296 --> 00:00:41.756 A:middle
This process can be
frustrating, but if you stick

00:00:41.756 --> 00:00:43.196 A:middle
with it, you can improve.

00:00:44.456 --> 00:00:46.966 A:middle
Research suggests five
key steps to guide you

00:00:46.966 --> 00:00:49.466 A:middle
on your path to development:
One.

00:00:49.876 --> 00:00:53.726 A:middle
Observe Your Current Skill
Level: Collect information

00:00:53.726 --> 00:00:54.676 A:middle
and assess yourself

00:00:54.676 --> 00:00:56.636 A:middle
on the skills you have
targeted for change.

00:00:57.476 --> 00:00:59.706 A:middle
Completing CapsimInbox
is a great first start!

00:01:00.996 --> 00:01:05.356 A:middle
Two. Set a Specific Goal:
Determine how much you need

00:01:05.356 --> 00:01:08.746 A:middle
to improve and focus on one key
behavior or skill at a time.

00:01:09.546 --> 00:01:11.546 A:middle
Avoid trying to do too
many things at once.

00:01:12.936 --> 00:01:16.686 A:middle
Three. Learn About the
Skill: Seek out information

00:01:16.686 --> 00:01:18.476 A:middle
to better understand the
skill you want to improve.

00:01:19.166 --> 00:01:20.586 A:middle
Find challenging situations

00:01:20.586 --> 00:01:22.286 A:middle
where you will have the
opportunity to learn

00:01:22.286 --> 00:01:23.766 A:middle
and practice your
targeted skill.

00:01:25.276 --> 00:01:27.926 A:middle
Four. Practice and
Seek Feedback:

00:01:28.876 --> 00:01:30.646 A:middle
Utilize all available
opportunities

00:01:30.646 --> 00:01:32.626 A:middle
to practice your
targeted skill and seek

00:01:32.626 --> 00:01:34.046 A:middle
as much feedback as possible.

00:01:34.256 --> 00:01:35.516 A:middle
Track your progress.

00:01:36.766 --> 00:01:41.106 A:middle
Five. Reward Yourself:
Provide yourself with rewards

00:01:41.106 --> 00:01:43.216 A:middle
that you find valuable
and are directly linked

00:01:43.216 --> 00:01:44.586 A:middle
to performing the desired skill.

00:01:44.776 --> 00:01:47.876 A:middle
It is important to keep
in mind these five steps,

00:01:48.106 --> 00:01:50.346 A:middle
even after you complete your
personal plan for improvement.

00:01:51.066 --> 00:01:53.906 A:middle
To help you; CapsimInbox
has incorporated these tips

00:01:53.906 --> 00:01:56.256 A:middle
into a self-guided process
that you can now begin.

00:01:56.666 --> 00:02:00.366 A:middle
To start building your
individual development plan -

00:02:00.366 --> 00:02:02.686 A:middle
"IDP" for short - first review

00:02:02.686 --> 00:02:04.576 A:middle
and evaluate your
skill scores below.

00:02:05.576 --> 00:02:07.046 A:middle
Skill definitions as well

00:02:07.046 --> 00:02:09.626 A:middle
as specific developmental
tactics are also provided

00:02:09.626 --> 00:02:10.556 A:middle
in the feedback report.

00:02:11.766 --> 00:02:13.816 A:middle
Once you've chosen a
specific skill to develop,

00:02:14.086 --> 00:02:16.736 A:middle
click on "improve,"
and you will be guided

00:02:16.736 --> 00:02:17.956 A:middle
through a self-directed process

00:02:17.956 --> 00:02:20.216 A:middle
that helps you build
an IDP customized

00:02:20.216 --> 00:02:21.836 A:middle
for your own developmental
success.

00:02:23.146 --> 00:02:24.326 A:middle
As you go through the process,

00:02:24.566 --> 00:02:26.176 A:middle
think about the goals
you want to achieve.

00:02:26.966 --> 00:02:28.566 A:middle
The more effort you
put into improving,

00:02:29.026 --> 00:02:30.666 A:middle
the more likely you
will be successful!

00:02:31.516 --> 00:02:31.956 A:middle
Good luck.

